						<div class="postbody">Well, it doesn't use an Arduino, but there's Rachel Simone Weil's <a href="http://www.nobadmemories.com/connectednes/" class="postlink">ConnectedNES</a>, which uses a <a href="https://www.particle.io/products/hardware/photon-wifi-dev-kit" class="postlink">Particle Photon</a> board.<br /><br />I'm not in a position to be able to judge the limitations of using external hardware, not having dealt with it myself. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_neutral.gif" alt=":|" title="Neutral" /></div>

