						<div class="postbody">Programming time depends on the specific part, but that sounds slow.<br /><br />The datasheet for the AT29C040A says that it should never take more than 10ms to program 256 bytes (Note 1 on page 6, tWC and the figure on page 7); it &quot;should&quot; only take 21 seconds to program that Flash.<br /><br />You could be limited by the interface to the programmer being too slow to feed data at the â‰ˆneeded 256kbit/sec.</div>

